                    <mxGeometry x="1230" y="888" width="26" height="26" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="34" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Internet&lt;/font&gt;" style="ellipse;shape=cloud;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F5F5F5;strokeColor=#157eb2;fontSize=11;fontColor=#5A6B7B;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontFamily=Helvetica;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1480" y="953" width="120" height="70" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="35" value="to the internet" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeWidth=2.5;strokeColor=#1B660F;rounded=1;fontSize=14;fontColor=#1B660F;entryX=0.16;entryY=0.55;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;entryPerimeter=0;" edge="1" parent="1" target="34">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
                        <mxPoint x="1308" y="990" as="sourcePoint"/>
                        <mxPoint x="1418" y="997" as="targetPoint"/>
                    </mxGeometry>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="36" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Steps&lt;br&gt;(0) DNS: the workload resolves squid-proxy.egress.internal via the Route 53 Resolver and the Lattice-managed Private Hosted Zone, which returns an IP managed by VPC Lattice.&lt;br&gt;(1) The workload (HTTP_PROXY set to squid-proxy.egress.internal on 3128) makes an outbound request to the VPC Lattice IP over TCP 3128, entering its Service Network.&lt;br&gt;(2) The service network forwards the raw TCP flow to the egress resource gateway, which targets the internal NLB DNS name.&lt;br&gt;(3) The resource gateway forwards to the internal NLB on its :3128 listener.&lt;br&gt;(4) The NLB sends the connection to a healthy Squid Fargate task.&lt;br&gt;(5) Squid applies the FQDN allowlist — permitted domains proceed; non-allowlisted domains are denied.&lt;br&gt;(6) Allowed traffic egresses to the internet via the Egress VPC NAT Gateway. The response returns along the same path.&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FBFBFB;strokeColor=#879196;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10;fontSize=14;fontColor=#232F3E;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="250" y="1080" width="1380" height="160" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
            </root>
        </mxGraphModel>
    </diagram>
</mxfile>